#  grafx2 keybindings
- D - freehand
- Z - Lines
- A - eyedropper
- W - Increase brush size
- Q - Decrease brush size
- X - Set brush to smallest
- T - Prev foreground color
- Y - Next foreground color
- <C-S> - Save file
- <C-Shift-S> Save as
- J - save cluster as brush (key, magic brush grab)
- G - show gridlines (hide or show the grid in magnify mode)

#  tablet
- 1 inc brush
- 2 dec brush
- 3 move

